      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence residuals monitored; solver error bounded at MRL 2 not required beyond residual reporting.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal solver error quantification beyond residual monitoring is not required. Residuals converged to 1e-5 for all equations; this factor is scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 planning."
