      "acceptanceCriteria": "User qualification and simulation procedure documentation reviewed at MRL 2 level.",
      "rationale": "MRL 2 does not require formal use error assessment beyond analyst qualification records. Analysts hold relevant CFD credentials; formal use error quantification is deferred consistent with MRL 2 scope."
