      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample characteristics (blood analog fluid properties) documented at MRL 2 level.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments used a glycerin-water blood analog; fluid properties are documented in the public dataset. Statistical characterization of sample variability is not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
