    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 planning. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The assessment team accepts the simulation evidence for the stated regulatory purpose.",
